name: GSI Pinnacle Backpacker Cookware
description: Ready, set, chow down. This convenient two-person, non-stick cookset is great for portability, durability and efficiency. The cookware is made from hard-anodized aluminum and Teflon® Radiance technology for awesome abrasion-resistance.Teflon Radiance enhances heat dispersion for quick and even heating.Clear nylon lid with integrated strainer is lightweight and durable. Silicone rim stands up to high temps.Includes 2L pot and a fry pan.Includes two insulated bowls and mugs.Includes folding pot gripper that locks and removes easily.Welded stuff sack doubles as a sink and wash basin.
